    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I tried this earlier in the summer and LOVED it. This afternoon I grabbed the chickpeas and parmesan, but also threw in some leftover pesto and toasted sunflower seeds (good if you like a little crunch) &#8211; YUM! Throw it all on a bed of spinach and life is truly good!</p>
    </div>

